WEBVTT

30:35.000 --> 30:36.040 line:80%
Tell them

30:36.040 --> 30:37.440 line:80%
we don't have to move anymore,

30:37.440 --> 30:38.860 line:80%
and give them some candy.

30:39.040 --> 30:40.670 line:80%
Then they won't laugh at you.

30:41.000 --> 30:41.870 line:80%
Changyu,

30:41.870 --> 30:44.480 line:80%
when will you go back to sleep with Zheng?

30:44.630 --> 30:46.490 line:80%
You're squeezing into my small bed
every day.
